                            <comment id="12777355" author="jukkaz" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2009 03:20:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good point, I didn&apos;t consider the performance impact when adding the language detection to AutoDetectParser.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve removed the feature from AutoDetectParser in revision 835720. Clients can still add language detection on top of the Parser API if they want, and it&apos;s probably best if we don&apos;t make it an integral part of the AutoDetectParser before the feature becomes more mature.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
